Description: Fragment of papyrus with 4 lines of Demotic text on recto, concerning animal omina. Same ms as EA 76623; P. Wien D 6218 and several unnumbered Berlin papyri, also Oxford and Brooklyn.
Curator's comments: To be published by Joachim Friedrich Quack (Heidelberg)
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (380686) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/380686)
